metadata.description:
A **[Genetic Chain](https://geneticchain.io)** Project.

**Project #8**: [Rainbow7 Pass](https://geneticchain.io/project/8) by Alejandro Mirabal

The Rainbow7 Pass provides holders with membership to the Genetic Chain Platform.  Passes will unlock access to pre-sales, free mints, future GC programs, as well as access to live events at the GC gallery.
